pullrequest.title: Learn Gazebo Visual Plugins for Ocean Reflections

content.raw:
I’m catching up on the changes here. There’s quite a bit going on. It looks like the latest commit is not what I should be looking at?

One suggestion, do you mind moving your code to a separate model and visual plugin? That way it’s easier to review the changes and make comments.
